title: BlackSky Signs Launch Deal With RocketLab For Next Gen Satellites
summary: BlackSky Technology Inc. (NYSE: BKSY) and Rocket Lab USA, Inc. (Nasdaq: RKLB) have announced the signing of a launch agreement for BlackSky's next generations satellites.

title: Redwire to supply cameras for True Anomaly’s inspector satellites
summary: True Anomaly, a startup based in Denver, will install Redwire’s navigation and sensing cameras on two inspector satellites it plans to launch next year.

title: Exotrail Expands To US To Serve Commercial and Government Customers
summary: Exotrail, a French space mobility company, has established two U.S. subsidiaries as part of its strategy to cater to the growing number of American clients.

title: Starfish Space wins Air Force contract to develop satellite guidance software
summary: Starfish Space has secured $1.8 million from the U.S. Air Force’s AFWERX technology accelerator to develop its satellite guidance software, the in-orbit servicing startup announced Aug. 8.
